text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me SBS' 'Flower Road' to come to an end + may continue second season in the future By jennywill 2 minutes ago 126 0 0 0 Google+ SBS ' ' Flower Road ' is coming to an end.
The show kicked off on ' V ' app first as a pilot and was scheduled to be a regular broadcast starting from September 5 of last year. It took its members on a journey on a 'flower' road and a 'dirt' road depending on the games. SBS revealed, " 'Flower Road' will be ending its first season. It'll come back to viewers with another season at a fitting time. "
